                                               rn-dtr-cge             .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * [giocon]                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/num/ioc/obj/ingiocon"
